---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Research — LurraGrid"
  description="LurraGrid's academic foundation: MTU PUSH program, Alfred P. Sloan Foundation, and the LurraCascade patent-pending continuity system."
>
  <Nav />

  <!-- Hero — full bleed blueprint/hologram image -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[75vh] flex flex-col justify-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/research-hero.jpg"
        alt="Engineering blueprints transitioning to holographic 3D mine shaft model"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        style="object-position: center 30%;"
      />
      <!-- Heavy top fade — protects nav -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.92) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.55) 15%, rgba(0,0,0,0.20) 35%, rgba(0,0,0,0.0) 55%);"></div>
      <!-- Bottom fade — lifts text -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.97) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.60) 35%, transparent 60%);"></div>
      <!-- Left darkening for text legibility -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.55) 0%, transparent 55%);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative px-8 md:px-12 pt-48 pb-24 max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full flex flex-col justify-center min-h-[75vh]">
      <p class="font-body text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6 animate-fade-up eyebrow-over-image">Academic Foundation</p>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-5xl md:text-7xl text-frost leading-none mb-6 animate-fade-up-delay-1">
        PEER-REVIEWED<br />FOUNDATION.
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-frost-dim max-w-xl leading-relaxed animate-fade-up-delay-2">
        LurraGrid is built on three years of multidisciplinary research. Not a concept. Not a simulation. A validated system with published prior art and a peer-reviewed engineering model.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="border-t border-rule mx-8 md:mx-12"></div>

  <!-- MTU PUSH -->
  <section class="py-24 px-8 md:px-12 reveal border-b border-rule section-blue-deep w-full">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <span class="font-display font-bold text-8xl text-rule">01</span>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8">
        <p class="font-body text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-royal mb-4">Michigan Technological University</p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-frost mb-6">MTU PUSH Program</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-base text-frost-dim leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The MTU Pumped Underground Storage Hydropower (PUSH) program conducted a three-year, multidisciplinary feasibility study of underground pumped hydro storage in the historic Mather B mine complex in Negaunee, Michigan. The program assembled specialists across mechanical engineering, hydrology, industrial archaeology, energy law, policy research, and mine geometry.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-base text-frost-dim leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The study included a full SolidWorks three-dimensional geometric model of the Mather B mine complex, hydrological analysis, legal and regulatory review, power market analysis, and community acceptance research. The team's findings confirmed the technical and commercial viability of the site.
        </p>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-royal pl-6">
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-frost leading-relaxed">
            The MTU PUSH team are original researchers and inventors. LurraGrid is the commercial application of their published work. They collaborate — LurraGrid does not direct them.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sloan -->
  <section class="py-24 px-8 md:px-12 reveal border-b border-rule section-blue-mid w-full">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <span class="font-display font-bold text-8xl text-rule">02</span>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8">
        <p class="font-body text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-royal mb-4">Institutional Funding</p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-frost mb-6">Alfred P. Sloan Foundation</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-base text-frost-dim leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The foundational research was funded by the Alfred P. Sloan Foundation under Grant G-2018-11305. The Sloan Foundation is one of the United States' most respected philanthropic institutions, with a long history of funding rigorous scientific and engineering research.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-base text-frost-dim leading-relaxed">
          Sloan funding is competitive, peer-reviewed at the grant level, and signals institutional confidence in the research team and thesis. The award covers the full three-year MTU PUSH study period.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 p-6 border border-rule">
          <p class="font-body text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-frost-dim mb-1">Grant Reference</p>
          <p class="font-display font-bold text-frost">G-2018-11305</p>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-frost-dim mt-1">Alfred P. Sloan Foundation</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LurraCascade patent -->
  <section class="py-24 px-8 md:px-12 reveal section-orange-accent w-full">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <span class="font-display font-bold text-8xl text-rule">03</span>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8">
        <p class="font-body text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-royal mb-4">Patent Pending</p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-frost mb-2 flex items-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
          LurraCascade Continuity System
          <span class="text-xs font-body tracking-widest uppercase border border-royal text-royal px-2 py-1">Patent Pending</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-frost-dim mb-8">USPTO Provisional Filing in Process</p>
        
        <p class="font-body text-base text-frost-dim leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The LurraCascade Continuity System solves the fundamental interruption problem in conventional underground pumped hydro: power delivery stops when the upper reservoir empties. LurraCascade uses a dual-reservoir threshold switching method to maintain continuous generation by automatically engaging a cascade stage at 20% reservoir level.
        </p>

        <p class="font-body text-base text-frost-dim leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Four independent patent claims are in process: the method, the system architecture, the behind-the-meter data center application, and the automated threshold actuator mechanism.
        </p>

        <div class="border border-rule p-8 mb-8">
          <p class="font-body text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-frost-dim mb-4">Prior Art Publication</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="font-body text-xs text-frost-dim w-24 shrink-0">Published</span>
              <span class="font-body text-sm text-frost">May 5, 2026</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="font-body text-xs text-frost-dim w-24 shrink-0">Repository</span>
              <span class="font-body text-sm text-frost">CERN Zenodo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="font-body text-xs text-frost-dim w-24 shrink-0">DOI</span>
              <a
                href="https://zenodo.org/doi/10.5281/zenodo.20045602"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="font-body text-sm text-royal hover:text-royal-light transition-colors duration-300"
              >
                10.5281/zenodo.20045602 ↗
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://zenodo.org/doi/10.5281/zenodo.20045602"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase px-8 py-3 border border-royal text-royal hover:bg-royal hover:text-frost transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          View Publication on Zenodo ↗
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>
